Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belakangan ini, rasanya\Nkau mengabaikan balas dendamku!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}H-Hah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebulan sejak penculikan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat kesaksian Kate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami mengetahui beberapa hal\Ntentang Daeg Gallus yang misterius.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kiriki kirikuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantra ajaib peninggalan Nona Lily
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah kata sandi\Nyang digunakan anggota mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tujuan mereka\Nadalah mencuri kunci Nona Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuserahkan kuncinya pada Tuan,\Ndan meminta dia menyelidikinya langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penculiknya bertato matahari\Ndan diyakini sebagai anggota mereka,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia dibunuh di penjara\Nsebelum sempat diinterogasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Mahkota Cecilia kabarnya\Nterlihat di sekitar lokasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:01:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kenapa kau ingin mengunjungi Abigail?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi bertemu Viscountess Aisha Huxley.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya kau mau bicara dengannya\Ndi pesta Nona Godwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau gadis sepertiku yang minta bertemu,\Ndia pasti akan mengabaikanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku akan meminjam\Nkekuatan Keluarga Duke O'Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah datang, Constance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang bertemu denganmu lagi, Nona Abigail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia cantik sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mata ametis dan gaun merah cerah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, dia tampak seperti putri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Matamu jeli juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham situasinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus pastikan surat pengantarmu\Nsegera sampai ke kediaman Huxley, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau percaya padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sikapmu memang aneh,\Ntapi masuk akal kalau ada Scarlett.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Scarlett, kau bisa mendengarku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Abby, dia ada di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Lucia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat sedih saat kau dieksekusi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, izinkan aku membantumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak usah melawak.\NMuka katakmu saja sudah jadi lelucon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya, "Tentu, aku mengerti."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa membayangkan\Ndia sedang menghinaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka ada orang lain\Nyang bisa melihat Scarlett.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keponakanku, Lucia,\Nmemang sensitif sejak lahir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau soal orang lain\Ndengan kemampuan serupa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada Viscount Hamsworth,\Nyang konon diberkati Dewi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diberkati Dewi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya Viscount\Nbisa melihat entitas supernatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau setuju, 'kan, Nona?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah itu sebabnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak peduli dengan babi itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo pergi, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan tanya tunanganmu\Nsoal masalah yang kudiskusikan tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku permisi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Theresa Jennings,\Nbunuh diri demi kekasihnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suaminya, Kevin Jennings,\Njadi pecandu narkoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kata Nona Abigail, Daeg Gallus\Nmenjual Surga Jakal, sejenis halusinogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang lebih penting adalah menanyai Aisha\Ntentang kejadian sepuluh tahun lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, seperti apa Aisha Huxley?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kupikir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulunya dia gadis suram\Nberpenampilan sederhana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salah satu pengikutku,\Natau lebih tepatnya, penggemarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku pakai gaun merah,\NAisha juga akan memakaianya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gaun biru jika aku pakai gaun biru,\Ndesainnya pun mirip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gaya rambutnya juga ditiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pernah menatap mataku\Ndan mengajak bicara tepat satu kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin menjadi sepertimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, apa jawabanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah sudah jelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia tak butuh dua Scarlett Castiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duke Castiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau rupanya, Randolph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada urusan mendesak apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kutanya langsung saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin tahu soal Cawan Suci Eris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak paham apa yang kau bicarakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang sekali, aku tak teringat apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma itu keperluanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, untuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuperingatkan kau\Nkarena aku sedang berbaik hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunjukkan kartumu\Nhanya setelah susunannya lengkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu rahasia agar panjang umur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita rangkum informasi yang ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, sepuluh tahun lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Upaya pembunuhan\Nterhadap Putri Mahkota Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Racun ditemukan dalam kendi air di vilanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa awalnya kau jadi tersangka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti kata putri berhati hitam itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua bermula saat di samping\Nkendi air Vila Ruzé,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ditemukan anting Pelangi Bulan\Nberdesain sama dengan milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebetulan, aku mengunjungi Vila Ruzé\Nbeberapa saat sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anting itu benar-benar milikmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat dituduh,\Naku bisa menunjukkan kedua antingku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lantas, apa kau...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja kuberi tahu penyidiknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya memakai barang unik\Nbuatan pengrajin khusus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyelidiki bengkel kerjanya\Nbisa menguatkan pernyataanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, kenapa kau tidak bebas\Ndari kecurigaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Analisis membuktikan satu anting\Nyang kuserahkan itu palsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka bilang\Naku pasti menyiapkan anting serupa,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena tahu akan diselidiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya, seseorang menyusup\Nke brankas Pasukan Pengaman,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menukar antingku dengan anting\Nyang ditemukan di lantai Vila Ruzé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pelakunya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi akhirnya, atas izin Yang Mulia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka menggeledah kediamanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tak bisa masuk kediaman Castiel\Ntanpa surat keputusan Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, seperti yang kau tahu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka menemukan botol racun\Nsetengah kosong di kamarku,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan itu menyebabkan aku ditangkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu Putri Cecilia\Ndalang di balik semua ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia yang paling diuntungkan\Ndari kematianku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, selama ini kupikir\Nsemua cuma sandiwaranya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jujur saja,\Nsekarang aku tidak begitu yakin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak melihatnya,\Ndia tampak tidak puas sedikit pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah sepuluh tahun,\Ndan sepertinya dia masih membenci Enrique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga tak terlihat\Nmengincar uang atau kekuasaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, apa motifnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya jalan kita\Nmenuju kebenaran masih panjang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bukan cuma soal masa lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuatu sedang terjadi saat ini,\Ndan Cecilia pasti terlibat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingat kata reporter rambut merah itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cecilia Ruzé adalah anak pelacur\Nyang berasal dari panti asuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kevin Jennings terlalu dekat\Ndengan kebenaran, lalu jadi pecandu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di hari Pangeran ke-7 Faris diculik,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pedagang itu mengunjunginya,\Ndan itu mustahil cuma kebetulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, aku yakin nama pedagang itu Vado.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi ingat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:10:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penculik dalam kesaksian itu\Npunya teman bernama Salvador.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ejaan namanya sangat mirip.\NApa itu kebetulan juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau mereka orang yang sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berarti Cecilia terhubung\Ndengan Daeg Gallus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya mereka juga dalang\Ndi balik Surga Jakal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang membanjiri Simpang Mawar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bangsawan yang pingsan\Ndi pesta Earl John Doe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chiara Grafton juga memiliki\Nhalusinogen yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu juga Kevin Jennings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, hilangnya Pangeran Ulysses\Ndan penculikan Kate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juga menyebarnya Surga Jakal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua itu ulah Daeg Gallus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melupakan satu hal penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga diserang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oleh Daeg Gallus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penculik Kate Lorraine\Nmencari kunci Lily, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi kubilang sesuatu sedang terjadi,\Ntapi itu tidak sepenuhnya benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari sepuluh tahun lalu hingga kini,\Nkejadian itu masih berlanjut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di Kerajaan Adelbide ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa eksekusiku\Nada hubungannya dengan hal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Lily mungkin dibunuh\Nkarena hal yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Hancurkan Cawan Suci Eris."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arti pesan terakhirnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami masih belum tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, Tuanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu Anda ingin berbagi info,\Ntapi kenapa ke ruang arsip?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluarga Orlamunde\Nmenyumbangkan beberapa barang di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir kita bisa menemukan\Npetunjuk terkait kunci itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga pernah ke sini bersama Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia biasa memanggilnya "Lily".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat tidak peka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kitab suci yang diberikan\Nkepada Santa Anastasia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari utusan Dewi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lapar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal permintaan Abigail,\Nitu akan memakan waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rumah sakit tempat Kevin Jennings dirawat\Nadalah milik Putri Mahkota.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada beberapa dokumen yang merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membahas kejadian sepuluh tahun lalu\Nbersama Scarlett.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bilang antingnya ditukar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memeriksa catatan terkait anting itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang dinyatakan palsu bukan Pelangi Bulan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}melainkan kerang\Nyang dikenal sebagai Cangkang Perak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan desainnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, Scarlett bertanya tentang desainnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang sangat mirip antingnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saluran distribusi\NCangkang Perak sangat dibatasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kuperiksa para pembelinya saat itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kutemukan nama keluarga yang tidak asing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluarga Count Spencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama gadis Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluarga Spencer memiliki sejumlah bengkel\Npembentuk logam mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aisha pasti bisa membuat anting\Nyang mirip dengan milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang akan pergi ke kediaman Huxley\Nuntuk bertanya padanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Y-Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada kemungkinan\Ndia berhubungan dengan Daeg Gallus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bertindak gegabah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar tak merasakan apa pun,\Njuga tak bisa mengingat apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku benar-benar dieksekusi di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Constance Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka dia akan menggunakan\NAbigail O'Brian untuk menghubungiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis biasa seperti dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa orang bilang\Ndia mirip Scarlett Castiel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada yang bisa menggantikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia adalah dewiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau Aisha Spencer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melihatku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru saja, dan juga tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, bagaimana kau bisa tahu namaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau memperkenalkan dirimu\Ndi pesta tempo hari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}K-Kau ingat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:15:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir kau bicara dengan siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang, Nona Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf membuatmu datang jauh-jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sekali tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih telah mengundangku,\NNona Huxley.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh mengejutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utusan Keluarga Duke O'Brian\Nmengunjungi properti sederhanaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski ternyata itu merupakan pengantar\Ndari Keluarga Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku perlu berbicara denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau boleh, aku ingin tanya\Nsatu hal dulu kepadamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, kalau memang bisa kujawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya bau apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada kenalanku yang punya ingatan\Ndan penciuman sangat tajam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tahu sejak kau melangkah keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong beri tahu aku, Nona Huxley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tubuhmu bau Surga Jakal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah Surga Jakal itu halusinogen\Nyang populer sepuluh tahun lalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kau salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang memakai parfum\Nyang agak tidak biasa hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu yang kau cium.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asalnya dari negeri jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar kalau kau tak tahu namanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pendusta ulung.\NAku sampai ingin tertawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}K-Kau sangat tidak sopan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cukup sampai di sini! Silakan pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marah karena ketahuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya kau ini apa, bocah kurang ajar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba sekali?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis di depanku masih orang yang sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi rasanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Camkan ini, Aisha Spencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang tidak sopan di sini\Nadalah kau yang mencoba menipuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir kau sedang bicara dengan siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Scarlett?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku takkan pernah\Nsalah mengenalinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepuluh tahun lalu,\NScarlett Castiel adalah pusat duniaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia dan tunangannya, Putra Mahkota Enrique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tak bersikap\Nlayaknya kekasih pada umumnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku tahu mereka nyaman\Nsatu sama lain seperti saudara kandung.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengagumi hubungan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kemudian wanita itu muncul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rumor cinta terlarang mereka\Nyang berbeda kasta
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menyebar dalam waktu singkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dibiarkan,\Nrumor itu akan jadi kenyataan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku perlu bertindak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikiran itu terlintas di benakku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlihat jauh lebih kurus\Ndaripada terakhir kali kita bertemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya ini stimulan dari luar negeri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Khasiatnya ajaib, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setetes saja cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kebanyakan, bisa merusak tubuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar Cecilia\Npunya tubuh lemah sejak lahir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kesehatannya menurun,\Ndia harus kembali ke wilayahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupakai anting tiruan\NPelangi Bulan milik Scarlett...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu pergi ke Vila Ruzé\Nmenjenguk dia yang sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa tahu Scarlett muncul\Nbeberapa saat sebelumnya
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan membuat keributan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kuisi kendi air ini\Ndengan stimulan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini demi Scarlett.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Scarlett pasti akan melakukan hal sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ini Scarlett...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melakukan ini akan membuatku\Nmenjadi Scarlett!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yang mencampur racun itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak tahu itu racun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Botol dari saat itu masih kusimpan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Analisis pasti membuktikan\Nitu cuma obat pelangsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan salahku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tolong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, Scarlett!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memaafkanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nkenapa kau tak akui saja dosamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak peduli itu racun atau bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu jelas aku tidak bersalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gara-gara perbuatanmu,\Naku dikirim ke tiang gantung.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku melakukannya demi dirimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ada kesempatan,\Nkau juga akan melakukan hal sama, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku, demi dirimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takkan pernah bertindak sehina itu,\Nmeski taruhannya nyawaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua kejadian sepuluh tahun lalu,\Nkau lakukan demi kepuasanmu sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berani-beraninya kau menjadikanku alasan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sadar dirilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aisha Spencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai hadiah,\Nkutanya untuk terakhir kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir kau sedang bicara dengan siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jauh di lubuk hati, aku sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah tahu jawabannya sejak lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma berpaling\Ndemi menyelamatkan diriku sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akulah penyebab segalanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membunuh Scarlett!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau memilih mati?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mati pun takkan menghapus\Nperbuatanmu pada Scarlett!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hiduplah dan tebus dosa-dosamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Huxley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beberapa hari kemudian, demi mengakui\Nkejahatannya sepuluh tahun lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aisha Huxley mengirim pesan ke Mayflower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:21:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia datang menjemputku?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aisha pelakunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia meracuni kendi air di Vila Ruzé.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada bukti fisiknya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya dia masih simpan botolnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari sepuluh tahun lalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membuktikannya akan memakan waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu... dia pakai Surga Jakal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Daeg Gallus terlibat dalam hal ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah tenang,\Nceritakan semua detailnya padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mengantarmu ke vila.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau hentikan dia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya kau biarkan dia mati di sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Connie bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau selamatkan dia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pelakunya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gara-gara dia, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya dia pakai kata-katamu\Nuntuk akhiri hidupnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menggunakanmu sebagai alasan\Nsampai akhir...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.95,0:23:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa biarkan itu terjadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Aisha mati sekarang,\Nkita bisa kehabisan petunjuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembalasanmu belum selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penukar anting itu,\NNona Lily, dan Daeg Gallus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua masih jadi misteri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar, Scarlett.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku rela habiskan sisa hidupku\Ndemi memastikan dendammu terbalas!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkadang ucapanmu ada benarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.83,0:23:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau jadi bersemangat, Connie.
